## API Endpoints

| Endpoint | Method | Purpose |
|----------|--------|---------|
| `/api/auth/login` | POST | Get JWT token |
| `/api/telemetry` | POST | Submit single telemetry |
| `/api/telemetry/batch` | POST | Submit multiple readings |
| `/api/telemetry` | GET | Query paginated data |
| `/api/telemetry/last` | GET | Get latest value |
| `/api/telemetry/chart-data/{deviceId}` | GET | Get chart-formatted data (24h) |
| `/api/telemetry/hourly/{deviceId}` | GET | Get hourly averages (10h) |

